SPELL NAME  : Resurrection
SPELL SYNTAX: Resurrect <target>
SPELL COST  : Special:  225 to cast, but takes a total of 450.
DESCRIPTION : This spells allows the caster to call upon the powers of
              Mitra and raise the target (player) from the dead.
              They might not get back everything they lost, but it
              will be far better than the normal means of praying.
              Resurrection of evil souls is possible, but Mitra will
              fill that person with her love and goodness. Players who
              have not gained her notice (level 8 and below) can't be
              resurrected at all.

              Note that Mitra holds a special place in her heart for her
              Clerics and Paladins so they can be resurrected at any
              level and their resurrections tend to be a bit more
              successful.
